<br />
<strong>Not Yet Using Revolution 2.3?</strong> <br />
Revolution 2.3 was a significant release. If you&#039;re not yet using it <a href="http://modx.com/blog/2014/07/15/revolution-2.3-brings-a-revamped-manager-user-experience-and-much-more/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">here&#039;s what you&#039;re missing out on</a>. <br />
<br />
<strong>It Takes a Village</strong> <br />
