To keep your MODX sites safe and performing their best, we strongly recommend upgrading to the latest version of Evolution. If you need someone to assist you with your MODX Evolution upgrade, check out our <a href="http://modx.com/professionals/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">MODX Professionals</a> directory for a MODX professional near you or <a href="http://modx.com/support-and-services/project-inquiry/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">contact us</a>. <br />
