<li>Fixed Manager login/Login security issue</li>
<li>Fixed incorrect sorting by rank in TV grid on template create/update screen</li>
<li>Fixed two display issues with the Element Tree related to Categories</li>
<li>Fixed to validation of Element Names</li>
